        {
            "title": "前美國財長薩默斯稱聯儲會政策「偏寬鬆」 通膨才是首要問題",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 前美國財政部長勞倫斯·<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:薩默斯;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/薩默斯\">薩默斯</a>表示，聯儲會政策正傾向於過於寬鬆，並強調美國經濟面臨的最大風險在於通膨而非就業市場。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「綜合考量所有金融狀況，我個人認為當前政策比人們認知的略為寬鬆，」薩默斯在彭博電視節目中對主持人David Westin表示。「風險平衡更偏向通膨而非失業。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">此番言論發表於聯儲會決策者一年來首次降息之後。聯儲會主席傑羅姆·鮑威爾表示，此舉反映了風險平衡的轉變，「就業成長大幅放緩及其他勞動力市場疲軟跡象」在近期數據中顯而易見。</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-c5d1f41d-6e2f-37fd-a6ee-bdb962f0732d-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「當前最大風險在於偏離2%通膨目標，使美國淪為通膨心理蔓延的國家，」身為哈佛大學教授兼彭博電視特約評論員的薩默斯強調。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「我認為當前貨幣政策及政策信號略顯寬鬆，」薩默斯補充道，「但這本質上是程度差異問題。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">薩默斯表示，「如果我處於鮑威爾主席的位置，我最擔心的就是通膨問題。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Summers Says Fed Policy ‘On the Loose Side,’ Inflation Top Issue</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
